caption: Some know bc y'all follow my Instagram that I've been really depressed lately and what just happened didn't make me feel better. I went to wash towels and I couldn't find the bleach so I asked my mom and she said"I can't trust you with the bleach. I will wash them. You have too much going on and I don't want you to do something you'll regret" I feel like dying now. I really need a hug from one of the boys or Jacqui or Amy or Amelie just anybody. She doesn't know that I breathed in the bleach fumes a couple weeks ago. Idk how she found out that I didn't wanna be here  anymore.
